{"tid":1625262,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［升級］全城轉用美金，將美金變成香港流通貨幣！","createTime":"2019-10-05T06:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T13:27:02.000Z","uid":53515,"like":113,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"37a4b43612c203f78badee1a26b7783af4aaf9d4","tid":1625262,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:25:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>點解咁做？</strong></span><br />\n1）控制貨幣，控制經濟。港紙一日盛行，香港政府嘅權力就仍然強大。但假如香港人用美金交易，變相將香港嘅經濟命脈直接送到美國手上，降低香港政府對香港人嘅控制能力！<br />\n<br />\n2）手上咁多現金唔用？經過尋晚政府繞過立法會、使用緊急法強行過左蒙面法，令到各區出現撳美金人潮，媒過得個擺字。<br />\n<br />\n3）<span style=\"color: red;\">用美金，有美軍</span>！我唔熟經濟，但我熟歷史。當年中東想用新貨幣取代美金做石油單位，結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>點樣做？</strong></span><br />\n首先，由小面額交易開始，用儲錢心態去做。如黃色經濟區內，買魚蛋用一美金交易。<br />\n等市面美元普及性提高，就可以向更大額交易出發。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>有咩成效？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1）《香港人開始轉用美金作流通貨幣！》依個媒體標題，正唔正？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）錢，係和理非最暴力嘅手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同時中產無法拒絕。可以令香港人多一個表態方式<br />\n<br />\n3）完全區分黃藍店。假如藍絲咁蠢，轉用美金交易，就由佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4）真攬炒。林鄭唔怕同全香港人開戰，但波叔都要補多句唔會搞外匯管制。<br />\n香港係世界最自由經濟體（曾經），我哋可以自由兌換同使用其他貨幣。<br />\n假設全香港都用美金=間接將香港交到美國手，等美國更有效控制香港（注意，對香港人未必有益，但中國一定反對）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>有咩風險</strong></span><br />\n我唔識，等經濟學家答<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>操作難道<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔識<br />\n<br />\n「譬如廚子做菜，有人品評他壞，他固不應該將廚刀鐵釜交給批評者，說道你試來做一碗好的看。」&mdash;&mdash;魯迅《對批評家的希望》"},{"pid":"be43bc1e779e91fe78dee661f547d06881a861d7","tid":1625262,"uid":5420,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:27:12.000Z","msg":"美金 美金 美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38df9ec2537e344ab5ab831c193c16e279a017c1","tid":1625262,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:27:52.000Z","msg":"夠薑就搞外匯管制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06b18511dbd47683989d8a9f8c543b47efea4c0","tid":1625262,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:28:06.000Z","msg":"我要用美金"},{"pid":"4b83f0d18546f49b21714122b3e826b601ff6d1e","tid":1625262,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:28:38.000Z","msg":"當香港變成美元區"},{"pid":"b94f51ba8acc5161d3451816a1c4dc3af1831cda","tid":1625262,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:29:29.000Z","msg":"我要用美金"},{"pid":"d40ef4bdd3ff055b76950667a050653f3f66e31b","tid":1625262,"uid":141947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:29:34.000Z","msg":"贊成贊成"},{"pid":"107e1d818619d75c0eb9a5b71585821c81d16ddc","tid":1625262,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"叫益絲轉用人民幣交易"},{"pid":"f8d1757385a9c568f552df90571b7dcc595ad29b","tid":1625262,"uid":5420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:32:32.000Z","msg":"美金 美金 美金"},{"pid":"86259bdf9c1c4d3aacab2fd55661077b0c37c69f","tid":1625262,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:32:42.000Z","msg":"將香港變成經濟戰嘅熱戰前線"},{"pid":"18fff8617bb9819ae57142069dabd4dff4e9f1e3","tid":1625262,"uid":53515,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:33:15.000Z","msg":"沙田（美